Package cn.crowdos.kernel

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CrowdKernel
    CrowdOS is a ubiquitous operating system for Crowdsoucring and Mobile Crowdsensing, which can deal with multiple types of crowdsourcing problems simultaneously.
    Decomposable<T>
    The Decomposable interface must be implement by any class that needs to be decomposed into smaller parts.
    Decomposer<T>
    A decomposer and decompose a object that implement Decomposable into multiple fine-grained parts.

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DecomposeException
    Thrown by Decomposer.decompose(int) to indicate something exceptions occurred during the decomposition operation.
    UninitializedKernelException
    Thrown to indicate that some operation has occurred on an uninitialized Kernel.
